OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776874270
OL,3,CLeicester City relegated from the
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FLeicester City have been relegated
OL,7,Ffrom the Championship after a 2-2 draw
OL,8,Fagainst Hull City.
OL,10,FThis follows a run of only one win in
OL,11,Ftheir last 16 games.
OL,13,FThey have now suffered back-to-back
OL,14,Frelegations, having finished 18th in
OL,15,Fthe Premier League last season.
OL,17,FThis relegation comes only ten years
OL,18,Fafter the club won the Premier League
OL,19,Fand six years after they won the FA
OL,20,FCup.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
