OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776874270
OL,3,CLeicester City relegated from the
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FThe Foxes would still have a fighting
OL,7,Fchance of staying in the division, if
OL,8,Fit weren't for a six-point deduction
OL,9,Fthey were given by the Premier League.
OL,11,FThe penalty came after the club was
OL,12,Ffound in breach of financial rules by
OL,13,Fthe Independent Disciplinary
OL,14,FCommission, appointed under Premier
OL,15,FLeague Rules, for having breached the
OL,16,FProfit and Sustainability Rules by
OL,17,Fmore than 20 million pounds over a
OL,18,Fthree-year reporting period ending
OL,19,Fwith the 2023/24 season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776874270
OL,3,CLeicester City relegated from the
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FBoth parties have submitted their
OL,7,Fappeals to the Chair of the Judicial
OL,8,FPanel.
OL,10,FAn Appeal Board will then be appointed
OL,11,Fto hear the case.
OL,13,FThe Premier League said: "To provide
OL,14,Fcertainty for all clubs and fans, (we)
OL,15,Fwill be seeking to have the appeal
OL,16,Fresolved urgently, and in any event
OL,17,Fbefore the end of the EFL season."
OL,19,FHowever, even without the points
OL,20,Fdeduction, the club would still be in
OL,21,Fthe relegation zone.
