OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776874270
OL,3,CLeicester City relegated from the
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FLeicester City have the most expensive
OL,7,Fsquad in the Championship with an
OL,8,Festimated market value of more than
OL,9,F#140 million.
OL,11,FThat makes their squad worth more than
OL,12,FCharlton Athletic, Portsmouth, Oxford
OL,13,FUnited, and Blackburn Rovers combined,
OL,14,Fwith all four of those teams sitting
OL,15,Fabove them in the table.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
